Moreover, formula_445 is a Radon measure with respect to the metric space topology and is uniform in the sense that every ball of the same radius (with respect to this metric) is of the same measure.

==Oriented Grassmannian==
This is the manifold consisting of all &quot;oriented&quot; formula_2-dimensional subspaces of formula_22. It is a double cover of formula_28 and is denoted by formula_449.

As a homogeneous space it can be expressed as:
