* Horniman Circle Gardens
* Jijamata Udyaan
* Jogger&#x27;s Park
* Joseph Baptista Gardens
* Kamala Nehru Park
* Mahalaxmi Racecourse
* Mahindra Hockey Stadium
* Middle Income Group Club Ground
* Oval Maidan
* Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel Indoor Stadium
* Shivaji Park
* Wankhede Stadium

