== Places of worship ==



=== Churches ===

* Afghan Church
* Cathedral of the Holy Name
* Church of Our Lady of Dolours, Wadala
* Church of Our Lady of Good Counsel &amp; Shrine of St. Anthony, Sion
* Church of Our Lady of Health, Cavel
