* St. Andrew&#x27;s Church
* St. John the Baptist Church
* St. Joseph&#x27;s Church, Juhu
* St. Michael&#x27;s Church
* St. Thomas Cathedral

=== Hindu temples ===
* Babulnath
* Jivdani Mata
* Jogeshwari Caves
* Kadeshwari Devi Temple
* Lalbaugcha Raja
* Mahalakshmi Temple
* Mumba Devi Temple
* Shaneshwar Sansthan
