* Siddhivinayak Temple
* Wagheshwari Temple
* Walkeshwar Temple

=== Masjid or shrines ===
* Haji Ali Dargah
* Jama Masjid
* Makhdoom Ali Mahimi
* Raudat Tahera

=== Synagogues ===
* Gate of Mercy Synagogue
* Knesset Eliyahoo
* Magen David Synagogue (Byculla)
* Nariman House

=== Others ===
* Global Vipassana Pagoda
* Godiji Parshwanath Jain Temple, Pydhonie
* Gurudwara Khalsa Sabha, Matunga

